* {{ill|Daiji (Japan)|ja|大治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1127|ja|1127|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|ja|源義光|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a military commander and younger brother of {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshiie|ja|源義家|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  (* {{ill|1045|ja|1045|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1433|ja|1433|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Komatsu|ja|後小松天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 100th emperor of the Northern Court (* {{ill|1377|ja|1377|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
