* {{ill|Hōreki|ja|Hōreki}} 10th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1760|ja|1760}}  {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日}} ） – {{ill|Kawaoka Seishū|ja|華岡青洲}} , a physician and pioneer of anesthesia († {{ill|1835|ja|1835}} ).
* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|lt=Bunka|lt_ja=文化}} 14th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1817|ja|1817}}  {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日}} ） – {{ill|Ono Yūgorō|ja|小野友五郎}} , a mathematician († {{ill|1898|ja|1898}} ).
* {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1849|ja|1849}}  {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日}} ） – {{ill|Saionji Kinmochi|ja|西園寺公望}} , who served as Prime Minister on two occasions and as genrō († {{ill|1940|ja|1940}} ).
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1871|ja|1871}}  {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日}} ） – {{ill|Doi Bansui|ja|土井晩翠}} , a poet († {{ill|1952|ja|1952}} ).

