{{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 23''' is the 23rd day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Kengan (Han)|ja|建安|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|200|ja|200|qq=}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=}} ） – During the Han, when Prince Shangchen’s rebellion occurred, the capital battle at Guandu took place as {{ill|Yuan Shao|ja|袁紹|qq=}} faced a night attack by {{ill|Cao Cao|ja|曹操|qq=}} . * {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|ja|Kōji|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1555|ja|1555|qq=}} {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|qq=}} ） – The era name was changed from {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文 (元号)|lt=Tenbun|lt_ja=天文|qq=}} to {{ill|Kōji|ja|Kōji|qq=}} . * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1577|ja|1577|qq=}} {{ill|December 2|ja|12月2日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=}} ordered {{ill|Hachiyoshi Hideyoshi|ja|羽柴秀吉|lt=Hideyoshi|qq=}} to launch an expedition against China. * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1629|ja|1629|qq=}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=}} ） – The Edo Shogunate banned female kabuki, female dance, and female jōruri for disrupting public order. * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|qq=}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1669|ja|1669|qq=}} {{ill|November 16|ja|11月16日|qq=}} ） – An Ainu chieftain, {{ill|Shakusha In|ja|シャクシャイン|qq=}} , was murdered during peace talks at Matsumae Taihira’s encampment. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=}} {{ill|December 8|ja|12月8日|qq=}} ） – The Meiji government’s general affairs were reorganized: for instance, {{Enomoto Takeaki|qq=}} and others occupied the Goryōkaku in Hakodate.
== Births == * {{ill|Genwa (Japan)|ja|元和|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1617|ja|1617|qq=}} {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Tosa Mitsuki|ja|土佐光起|qq=}} , a painter († {{ill|1691|ja|1691|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Hōreki|ja|Hōreki|qq=}} 10th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1760|ja|1760|qq=}} {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Kawaoka Seishū|ja|華岡青洲|qq=}} , a physician and pioneer of anesthesia († {{ill|1835|ja|1835|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|lt=Bunka|lt_ja=文化|qq=}} 14th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1817|ja|1817|qq=}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Ono Yūgorō|ja|小野友五郎|qq=}} , a mathematician († {{ill|1898|ja|1898|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1849|ja|1849|qq=}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Saionji Kinmochi|ja|西園寺公望|qq=}} , who served as Prime Minister on two occasions and as genrō († {{ill|1940|ja|1940|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=}} {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Doi Bansui|ja|土井晩翠|qq=}} , a poet († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshōjingo|ja|Tenpyō神護|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|765|ja|765|qq=}} {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Junnin|ja|淳仁天皇|qq=}} , the 47th emperor. * {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|qq=}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1669|ja|1669|qq=}} {{ill|November 16|ja|11月16日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Shakusha In|ja|シャクシャイン|qq=}} , the Ainu chief. * {{ill|Taihei Kōkoku|ja|太平興国|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|976|ja|976|qq=}} {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Zhao Kuangyin|ja|趙匡胤|qq=}} (Taizu), the first emperor of the Northern Song (* {{ill|927|ja|927|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Daiji (Japan)|ja|大治|qq=}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1127|ja|1127|qq=}} {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|ja|源義光|qq=}} , a military commander and younger brother of {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshiie|ja|源義家|qq=}} (* {{ill|1045|ja|1045|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1433|ja|1433|qq=}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Komatsu|ja|後小松天皇|qq=}} , the 100th emperor of the Northern Court (* {{ill|1377|ja|1377|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1856|ja|1856|qq=}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳|qq=}} , an agrarian reformer (* {{ill|1787|ja|1787|qq=}} ).
