'''October 23''' is the 23rd day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|12=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Kengan (Han)|ja|建安|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|200|ja|200|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – During the Han, when Prince Shangchen’s rebellion occurred, the capital battle at Guandu took place as {{ill|Yuan Shao|ja|袁紹|qq=|12=draft}}  faced a night attack by {{ill|Cao Cao|ja|曹操|qq=|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|ja|Kōji|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1555|ja|1555|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – The era name was changed from {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文 (元号)|lt=Tenbun|lt_ja=天文|qq=|12=draft}}  to {{ill|Kōji|ja|Kōji|qq=|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1577|ja|1577|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|December 2|ja|12月2日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=|12=draft}}  ordered {{ill|Hachiyoshi Hideyoshi|ja|羽柴秀吉|lt=Hideyoshi|qq=|12=draft}}  to launch an expedition against China.
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1629|ja|1629|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – The Edo Shogunate banned female kabuki, female dance, and female jōruri for disrupting public order.
* {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|qq=|12=draft}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1669|ja|1669|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 16|ja|11月16日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – An Ainu chieftain, {{ill|Shakusha In|ja|シャクシャイン|qq=|12=draft}} , was murdered during peace talks at Matsumae Taihira’s encampment.
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|December 8|ja|12月8日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – The Meiji government’s general affairs were reorganized: for instance, {{Enomoto Takeaki|qq=}}  and others occupied the Goryōkaku in Hakodate.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Genwa (Japan)|ja|元和|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1617|ja|1617|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tosa Mitsuki|ja|土佐光起|qq=|12=draft}} , a painter († {{ill|1691|ja|1691|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Hōreki|ja|Hōreki|qq=|12=draft}} 10th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1760|ja|1760|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kawaoka Seishū|ja|華岡青洲|qq=|12=draft}} , a physician and pioneer of anesthesia († {{ill|1835|ja|1835|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|lt=Bunka|lt_ja=文化|qq=|12=draft}} 14th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1817|ja|1817|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ono Yūgorō|ja|小野友五郎|qq=|12=draft}} , a mathematician († {{ill|1898|ja|1898|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1849|ja|1849|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Saionji Kinmochi|ja|西園寺公望|qq=|12=draft}} , who served as Prime Minister on two occasions and as genrō († {{ill|1940|ja|1940|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Doi Bansui|ja|土井晩翠|qq=|12=draft}} , a poet († {{ill|1952|ja|1952|qq=|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Tenshōjingo|ja|Tenpyō神護|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|765|ja|765|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Junnin|ja|淳仁天皇|qq=|12=draft}} , the 47th emperor.
* {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|qq=|12=draft}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1669|ja|1669|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 16|ja|11月16日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Shakusha In|ja|シャクシャイン|qq=|12=draft}} , the Ainu chief.
* {{ill|Taihei Kōkoku|ja|太平興国|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|976|ja|976|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Zhao Kuangyin|ja|趙匡胤|qq=|12=draft}}  (Taizu), the first emperor of the Northern Song (* {{ill|927|ja|927|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Daiji (Japan)|ja|大治|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1127|ja|1127|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|ja|源義光|qq=|12=draft}} , a military commander and younger brother of {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshiie|ja|源義家|qq=|12=draft}}  (* {{ill|1045|ja|1045|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1433|ja|1433|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Komatsu|ja|後小松天皇|qq=|12=draft}} , the 100th emperor of the Northern Court (* {{ill|1377|ja|1377|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1856|ja|1856|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳|qq=|12=draft}} , an agrarian reformer (* {{ill|1787|ja|1787|qq=|12=draft}} ).

