'''October 23''' is the 23rd day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|qq=}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomobiki|qq=}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Kengan (Han)|ja|建安|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kengan (Han)|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|200|ja|200|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/200|qq=}}  {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 17|qq=}} ） – During the Han, when Prince Shangchen’s rebellion occurred, the capital battle at Guandu took place as {{ill|Yuan Shao|ja|袁紹|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yuan Shao|qq=}}  faced a night attack by {{ill|Cao Cao|ja|曹操|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Cao Cao|qq=}} .
* {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|ja|Kōji|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōji (Japan)|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1555|ja|1555|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1555|qq=}}  {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 7|qq=}} ） – The era name was changed from {{ill|Tenbun|ja|天文 (元号)|lt=Tenbun|lt_ja=天文|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenbun|qq=}}  to {{ill|Kōji|ja|Kōji|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōji|qq=}} .
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1577|ja|1577|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1577|qq=}}  {{ill|December 2|ja|12月2日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 2|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobunaga|qq=}}  ordered {{ill|Hachiyoshi Hideyoshi|ja|羽柴秀吉|lt=Hideyoshi|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hachiyoshi Hideyoshi|qq=}}  to launch an expedition against China.
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1629|ja|1629|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1629|qq=}}  {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 7|qq=}} ） – The Edo Shogunate banned female kabuki, female dance, and female jōruri for disrupting public order.
* {{ill|Kanbun|ja|寛文|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanbun|qq=}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1669|ja|1669|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1669|qq=}}  {{ill|November 16|ja|11月16日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 16|qq=}} ） – An Ainu chieftain, {{ill|Shakusha In|ja|シャクシャイン|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakusha In|qq=}} , was murdered during peace talks at Matsumae Taihira’s encampment.
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}}  {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1868|qq=}}  {{ill|December 8|ja|12月8日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 8|qq=}} ） – The Meiji government’s general affairs were reorganized: for instance, {{Enomoto Takeaki|qq=}}  and others occupied the Goryōkaku in Hakodate.

