* {{ill|Kanbun (era)|en|Kanbun (era)|WD=Q1146228|lt=Kanbun|1=Kanbun (era)}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1669|en|1669|WD=Q7602|lt=1669|1=1669}}  {{ill|November 16|en|November 16|WD=Q3029|lt=November 16|1=November 16}} ） – An Ainu chieftain, {{ill|Shakusha In|ja|シャクシャイン|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakusha In|comment=changed title based on wikidata|1=Shakushain|WD=Q3280296}} , was murdered during peace talks at Matsumae Taihira’s encampment.
* {{ill|Meiji era|en|Meiji era|WD=Q3125096|lt=Meiji era|1=Meiji era}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1868|en|1868|WD=Q7717|lt=1868|1=1868}}  {{ill|December 8|en|December 8|WD=Q2301|lt=December 8|1=December 8}} ） – The Meiji government’s general affairs were reorganized: for instance, {{Enomoto Takeaki|qq=}}  and others occupied the Goryōkaku in Hakodate.

